+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014dW8UfanDXthonyTQQZtMU","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Project Structure Overview\n\nHere's a complete picture of what's set up in `/workspace`:\n\n### Project Metadata\n- **Name**: bench-collab-server\n- **Version**: 1.0.0\n- **Description**: Real-time collaborative editing benchmark\n- **Type**: ES Module (Node.js)\n- **Category**: Greenfield/Complex task with 30-minute timeout\n\n### Directory Structure\n```\n/workspace/\n├── src/                          (empty - to be implemented)\n├── .git/                         (version control)\n├── .thunderdome/                 (testing/grading config)\n├── node_modules/                 (dependencies installed)\n├── dist/                         (compiled output - .gitignored)\n├── TASK.md                       (requirements)\n├── package.json                  (dependencies & scripts)\n├── tsconfig.json                 (TypeScript config)\n├── vitest.config.ts             (test framework config)\n├── .eslintrc.cjs                (linting rules)\n├── schema.sql                    (SQLite database schema)\n└── .gitignore                    (git exclusions)\n```\n\n### Dependencies & Tech Stack\n\n**Production Dependencies**:\n- `ws` (^8.18.0) - WebSocket server\n- `better-sqlite3` (^11.0.0) - SQLite database\n- `express` (^4.21.0) - HTTP server\n\n**Dev Dependencies**:\n- `typescript` (^5.4.0) - TypeScript compiler\n- `vitest` (^2.0.0) - Test runner\n- `@vitest/coverage-v8` (^2.0.0) - Coverage reporting\n- `eslint` + TypeScript plugins - Code linting\n- `supertest` (^7.0.0) - HTTP testing\n- Type definitions for ws, better-sqlite3, express, supertest\n\n### TypeScript Configuration\n\n**tsconfig.json** settings:\n- Target: ES2022\n- Module: Node16\n- Output: `/workspace/dist/`\n- Input: `/workspace/src/**/*`\n- Strict mode: enabled\n- Source maps & declarations: enabled\n- Excludes: node_modules, dist, tests\n\n### Database Schema (schema.sql)\n\nThree tables defined:\n1. **documents** - Title, content, timestamps\n2. **versions** - Version history with operation tracking\n3. **active_connections** - Track concurrent WebSocket connections\n\n### NPM Scripts\n- `npm run build` - Compile TypeScript\n- `npm run lint` - Run ESLint\n- `npm run test` - Run Vitest tests\n\n### Grading Criteria (45 total tests, 100 points)\n1. **Build** (10 pts) - TypeScript compilation\n2. **Lint** (5 pts) - ESLint validation\n3. **REST CRUD** (15 pts) - 10 tests for document management\n4. **WebSocket Lifecycle** (15 pts) - 8 tests for connection management\n5. **Single Client Editing** (10 pts) - 6 tests for basic operations\n6. **Two-Client Convergence** (20 pts) - 8 tests for conflict resolution (OT)\n7. **Stress Test** (15 pts) - 5 tests for 10 concurrent clients\n8. **Error Handling** (5 pts) - 5 tests for error scenarios\n9. **Persistence** (5 pts) - 3 tests for data survival across restarts\n\n**Pass threshold**: 70 points\n\n### Key Requirements\n\nThe implementation must export a `createApp` factory function from `src/server.ts` (or `src/index.ts`) that returns an object with:\n- `app` - Express application\n- `start(port?)` - Start listening, return actual port\n- `stop()` - Graceful shutdown\n\nThe system needs to handle:\n- REST API for CRUD operations with document versioning\n- WebSocket real-time collaboration with operation broadcasting\n- Conflict resolution using Operational Transform (OT) or CRDTs\n- SQLite persistence\n- Robustness with 10+ concurrent clients\n\n### Git Status\n- Current branch: HEAD\n- Main branch: main\n- Untracked files: `.thunderdome-output.jsonl`, `.thunderdome-stderr.log`\n- Starting commits: 064cc8d (initial) and 2dc69c3 (greenfield: remove tests, rewrite TASK.md)\n\nThe `/workspace/src/` directory is completely empty and ready for implementation."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a9ca92f (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens